<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَإِيَّاكَ وَالْهَمَّازَ إِنْ قُمْتَ عَنْهُ وَالْـ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بَذِيَّ فَإِنَّ الْمَرْءَ بِالْمَرْءِ يَقْتَدِي<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلا تَصْحَبِ الْحَمْقَى فَذُو الْجَهْلِ إِنْ يَرُمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>صَلاحًا لأَمْرٍ يَا أَخَا الْحَزْمِ يُفْسِدِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَخَيْرُ مَقَامٍ قُمْتُ فِيهِ وَخِصْلَةٍٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تَحَلَّيْتَهَا ذِكْرُ الإِلَهِ بِمَسْجِدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَكُفَّ عَنْ الْعَوَرَا لِسَانَكَ وَالْيَكُنْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>دَوَامًا بِذِكْرِ اللهِ يَا صَاحِبِي نَدِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَحَصِّنْ عَنْ الْفَحْشَا الْجَوَارِحَ كُلِّهَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَكُنْ لَكَ فِي يَوْمِ الْجَزَا خَيْرَ شُهَّدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَحَافِظْ عَلَى فِعْلِ الْفُرُوضِ بِوَقْتِهَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَخُذْ بِنَصِيبٍ فِي الدُّجَا مِنْ تَهَجُّدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَنَادِ إِذَا مَا قُمْتَ بِاللَّيْلِ سَامِعًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>قَرِيبًا مُجِيبًا بِالْفَوَاضِلِ يَبْتَدِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَمُدَّ إِلَيْهِ كَفَّ فَقْرِكَ ضَارِعًا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>بِقَلْبٍ مُنِيبٍ وَادْعُ تُعْطَ وَتَسْعَدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلا تَسْأَ مَنَّ الْعِلْمِ وَاسْهَرْ لِنَيْلِهِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِلا ضَجَرٍ تَحْمِدْ سُرَى اللَّيْلِ فِي غَدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَلا تَطْلُبَنَّ الْعِلْمَ لِلْمَالِ وَالرِّيَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَإِنَّ مِلاكَ الأَمْرِ فِي حُسْنِ مَقْصَدِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَكُنْ عَامِلاً بِالْعِلْمِ فِيمَا اسْتَطَعْتَهُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>